name: GARDEN TOYZ COLLECTION - [M0URN1N6 64RD3N]
description: Thoughts and ideas overwhelm him in the morning. He is full of energy and strength to accomplish everything he has planned, to turn the world upside down. Nothing binds him, all the restraining mechanisms are illusory - they exist inside his consciousness. He has a rich imagination and a razor-sharp mind, which is clouded only by the voices he hears before waking up.
